{
  "stem": "7093.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she sent me up to the headmistress.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the headmistress called in my mother, said what a terrible person I am and what a terrible crime I committed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I must say, later on, I became very friendly with this young man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It wasn't worthwhile.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He was a very nice chap, but definitely not worthwhile being persecuted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because from that moment on by this history teacher, I was persecuted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, and every single time she came into the class, we had to get up and then sit down.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the first thing, [NON-ENGLISH] get up, your lesson.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I swotted the whole afternoon before history lesson.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I couldn't get out a word.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I just went blank.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I didn't remember anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And she was the most anti-Semitic teacher altogether.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I mean, she was absol-- and she married, actually, the, the most-- the biggest anti-Semite in town, the leader of the-- the Arrow-- Arrow Cross.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "In Hungary, Arrow Cross was what the swastika was in Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Arrow Cross was in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he was the leader of the Arrow Cross band.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And she married him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And she was an absolutely vicious woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I was a nasty girl, because at the age of 15, I sent her a box, a dead rat in a box with a pink ribbon, and then another box and a red ribbon, and another box with a blue ribbon.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I did it anonymously.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And in a way, I'm still ashamed of it, that I did it anonymously.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But I'm happy I did it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But she was an absolutely-- and I, I, later on, I mean after the war, I checked up that this [INAUDIBLE] from-- this is French teacher.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
